Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:27.83,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right! Fine, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:30.54,sign_3545_65_If_there_are__h3,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz353\frx2\fry350}If there are\N{\c&H2C3835&}\h3 evil spirits,\N\hthe exorcism\N\h\hfee on 1 of \N\h\hthem will be\N\h\hon the house!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:30.54,Main,Customer 1,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! I knew it'd be worth the trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.46,Main,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,226)\frz263\fs12\c&H052013&\3c&HBACDD3&\shad0\an7\pos(144,92)}The Spiritual Compendium  17th Edition
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.71,Main,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,268)\an9\frz267\fs8\c&H081404&\3c&HD6D7D9&\shad0\pos(178,356)}~The Miraculous Unknown Psychic~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.76,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But this is the only time I'm doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.76,0:02:34.92,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't be held responsible\Nfor what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:35.75,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:46.19,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this on your person at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.77,sign_3958_73_Curse,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Curse
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:48.80,Main,Customer 1,0000,0000,0000,,The hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.73,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cursed, well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:54.38,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you have that with you, \NI'm sure something will happen someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:55.47,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't need any payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:58.44,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,But just make sure you don't \Ntell anyone else about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:00.47,Main,Customer 1,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I believe you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:03.16,Main,Customer 1,0000,0000,0000,,but if you're messing with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:06.49,Main,Customer 1,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to curse you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.62,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Man, he finally left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:15.29,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I can understand hating someone \Nso much you want to curse them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.46,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have someone like that too, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.78,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:20.62,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.37,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Someone I want to curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:27.47,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, you don't need to think \Nso hard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:33.38,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.18,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Can't think of anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:37.15,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take so long, then!\N You actually scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:41.03,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, was it a good idea\Nto give him that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:43.57,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just cooked it up on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.37,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it won't harm anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:48.06,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:49.33,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.75,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's a lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.75,sign_5557_99_First_in_the_wor,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,First in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.75,sign_5557_91___Goku_NERO____0,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,- Goku NERO -\N\N{\b0\fs10}0 Purine\N0 Carbs\N\N\NAlcohol 4%
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.75,sign_5557_101_Pork_Loin_Tonkat,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Pork Loin Tonkatsu Bento
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:55.36,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,in his mind, he believes that he's \Nactually cursing someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:58.94,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to keep living\Nunder that impression?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:03.22,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that rather frightening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:04.68,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Mob?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:09.39,sign_5867_106_Reigen_Arataka,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Reigen Arataka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:09.39,sign_5867_105_The_New_Star_of_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The New Star of the 21st Century
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:09.39,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's rare... He's actually \Nvoicing his own opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:13.48,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Something's obviously bothering him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:15.52,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Did I miss something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:19.07,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is Spirits and \NSuch Consultation Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:21.88,Main,reigen,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.81,Main,Customer 2,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I thought it was a stalker,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.92,Main,Customer 2,0000,0000,0000,,so I talked to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:32.29,Main,Customer 2,0000,0000,0000,,But it just didn't seem human...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.25,Main,Customer 2,0000,0000,0000,,It was staring at me through \Nthe window the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:36.46,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,The window?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.34,sign_6765_117_Seasoning_Moving,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Seasoning Moving Center
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:51.31,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the fifth floor,\Nand there's no balcony... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.22,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,You here, Dimple?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:53.69,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,The hell do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.39,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Could you check things out\Naround this window?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:58.61,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,See if there's a rope or something \Ndangling from the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.65,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,And why do I have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.57,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to eat any evil spirits you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.33,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Mob, do you sense anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.28,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, though it's faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:10.70,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, not a damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:13.16,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell did you close \Nthe window, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:16.75,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,But there definitely \Nseems to be a stalker...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:21.18,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of interest would a ghost\Nhave in a living woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:25.51,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me. It's pretty rare for spirits\Nto have any sexual desires left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.76,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like they can reproduce anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.85,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,But does love always have to \Ncome with sexual desires?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:33.10,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I don't want to\Ndiscuss this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.98,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Right back at you, ya jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:42.86,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... a poltergeist?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:47.32,Main,Customer 2,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do? It must be mad\NI called you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:50.50,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Did it settle down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.00,Main,Customer 2,0000,0000,0000,,Outside the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.42,Main,Customer 2,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:02.51,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Mob! Vaporize it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:03.88,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:06.05,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,a living person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:07.51,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,So it is a stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:10.22,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:17.86,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,He's in the next apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.18,Main,Neighbor,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12}Who are these people? Why are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:29.30,Main,Neighbor,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12}It's not like I did anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:33.41,Main,Neighbor,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, yeah, I'm sorry I used an \Nout of body experience to spy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:36.58,Main,Neighbor,0000,0000,0000,,But I seriously fell for you at first sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:41.07,Main,Neighbor,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt like this before... \NI didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.41,Main,Neighbor,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... I'm serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.01,Main,Neighbor,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go out with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.55,Main,Neighbor,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way! I'll murder you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.30,Main,Neighbor,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.51,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,You pervy peeping tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.47,Main,Neighbor,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, owie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:02.09,Main,Neighbor,0000,0000,0000,,Say no to violence! Let me go! \NI'll call the cops, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:03.31,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:06.85,Main,Neighbor,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I was in the wrong! \NI'll never do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:08.07,Main,Neightbor,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:11.13,Main,Neighbor,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings for you are genuine, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.76,Main,Neighbor,0000,0000,0000,,So, please... p-p-p-p...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:13.96,Main,Customer 2,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:18.62,Main,Customer 2,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously insanely creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:28.08,Main,Customer 2,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I was scared of {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:31.74,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,So he tried to hide his stalking tendencies\Nbehind a supernatural phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:33.51,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try that at home, Shigeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:34.94,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:39.78,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she feel so differently after finding\Nout it was a human and not an evil spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:40.73,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:44.02,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Man, he's got a lot on his mind today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.09,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll pick his brain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:49.70,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's head back\Nand grab some soba on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:51.57,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:57.32,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:58.58,Main,College student B,0000,0000,0000,,We were waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:01.18,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you sure got him working \Na long part-time shift today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.05,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Three jobs in one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:04.79,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,That website is paying off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:09.33,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,We want to make some memories \Nbefore we graduate, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:13.95,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,So, like, we want to go to some popular \Nhaunted place and take a spirit photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:16.02,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But it'd suck if we actually\Nran into an evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.30,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,So they're just messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.38,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like I'm \Ngoing to turn them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:20.52,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,When and where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:23.44,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, my dude! \NWe've got a car waiting just outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.91,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,They definitely don't have a plan in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:32.07,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to getting there in\N20 minutes? It's already been 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:34.86,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,I think it might take another 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.78,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,We might not have time for soba after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:39.85,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So who the heck are you? His assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:41.11,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a part-timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:43.76,Main,College student B,0000,0000,0000,,You work part-time at a psychic's office?\N That's hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.76,0:08:45.00,Main,College student b,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.00,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Mob!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.92,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate. Make sure you're \Nprepared for the unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:48.67,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.00,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you sound legit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:54.87,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.92,Main,College student B,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! This place is creepy AF!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.99,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,OMG! I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:03.98,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,Holy shit, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:03.98,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.34,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,You sense any spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.64,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Faintly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:26.85,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't deserve to be\Na popular haunted spot, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:29.87,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,All right, hurry up and \Ntake that picture, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.18,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:34.51,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:37.89,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, say chee— \NActually, could you take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:41.58,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,I want to vehemently decline, \Nbut they're customers, so what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:42.61,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, say chee—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:44.98,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, don't forget the flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:47.06,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, say cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:54.64,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,We should head back. \NMy disciple's still in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:55.85,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:57.41,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,TYVM.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:57.41,Main,College student B,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:59.91,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Also, regarding the fee...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:01.53,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,What? Fee?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:03.24,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What are you even talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:05.91,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,What? The fee for this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:09.64,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing bad happened, and you\Ndidn't even do anything, psychic dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:11.88,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,You really want us to pay you for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.61,Main,College student B,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a scam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:15.84,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like, a total scam!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:20.55,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,No pay, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:22.83,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a ride back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.02,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. I'd say the unexpected just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:29.00,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. Let's head out to \Nthe road and hail us a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.48,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,No soba tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.07,Show_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx60\fscy200\fad(942,1)\fs24\pos(370,14)\c&HB5705A&}Mob Psycho 100
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:45.58,Show_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx60\fscy200\fs22\c&HDADA83&\pos(150,165)}Mob Psycho 100
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:52.72,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:54.24,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:55.75,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,You ignoring me? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:11:00.66,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you, stumbling around.\N You're in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:02.51,Main,Student B,0000,0000,0000,,But since you're here, \Ncould you lend us some cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.43,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:05.99,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Why you freakin' out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:07.85,Main,Student B,0000,0000,0000,,Could you bring us some money tomorrow, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:08.50,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:09.81,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,You heard the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:15.83,Main,Student B,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Sugimoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.91,Main,Student B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:22.77,Main,Student B,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you stripping, Sugimoto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.20,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:31.92,Main,Student B,0000,0000,0000,,Sugimoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.46,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Dimple, stop! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.07,Main,Student B,0000,0000,0000,,Sugimoto... Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:39.81,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:41.51,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:43.34,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try this again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:47.12,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you little shit! \NYou were laughing just now, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:48.44,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:50.73,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You get what this is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:52.42,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,We're mugging yo—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:56.77,Main,Student B,0000,0000,0000,,Sugimoto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:03.94,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay! Let him go, Ritsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:05.41,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.79,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,They seem like a bad crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:11.44,Main,Student B,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, what's wrong with you, Sugimoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.32,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Did you need something from our club member?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:21.09,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.03,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who the hell are you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:25.51,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Who said you could surround \Nme like that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.60,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:28.97,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kick yer asses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:32.69,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop squishing me, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:35.42,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I can't get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:38.09,Main,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:41.11,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm fine, so please don't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:42.78,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:44.78,Main,Student B,0000,0000,0000,,Sugimoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:47.36,Main,Student B,0000,0000,0000,,You'll regret this, you jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:49.83,Main,Tenga,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.45,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:54.22,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,You need to know when to \Nfight back, Kageyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.62,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Or they're just going to try \Nto bully you even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.42,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of a good way to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:01.63,Main,Tenga,0000,0000,0000,,Kick their asses with your \Nshadow leader powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:06.20,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to waste your powers\Non guys like them, Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.35,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,If they show up again, I'll get rid of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:13.81,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Raking bad guys over the coals is \Nwhat's good for them and society.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:16.37,Main,Tenga,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you kick their \Nasses on your own next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:18.27,Main,Tenga,0000,0000,0000,,You've got the power to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:22.94,sign_4283_38_Spirits_and_Such,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\frz266\fs14\3c&H282725&\pos(419,60)}Spirits and Such Consultation Office
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:26.16,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,What? You ended up with a spirit photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:29.83,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... So we wanted to \Nask for your help again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:33.75,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Just throw some salt around. \NI don't do volunteer work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:36.62,Main,College student B,0000,0000,0000,,We're really sorry! We'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:39.84,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:42.95,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,We want to go back to that haunted place
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:46.26,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,and have you make the ghost \Nin this picture disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:52.14,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I can exorcise that \Nphotograph if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.06,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even need to go back to the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:58.38,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No way! It's creepy enough \Nknowing that thing exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:13:59.27,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Please get rid of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:02.63,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,So an exorcism request. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:04.23,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain the various options.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:06.23,Main,College student B,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take the most expensive one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:11.41,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you got dragged out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.39,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,And your Sunday got ruined yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:14.98,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,You can get pissed off about this, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.48,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,Please wrap this up as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:48.73,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,There're three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:51.28,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,They don't seem to be evil spirits, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:54.81,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to take care of them. \NThey're scaring our clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.00,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and exorcise them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:58.76,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:07.71,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us are family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:11.53,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We died in an accident and\Nlost our chance at a good life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:17.02,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But now that we're ghosts,\Nwe've been living here peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.97,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't done anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:24.16,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I just want... to stay with my \Nfamily a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:30.03,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as this desire is fulfilled,\N we will disappear naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:33.66,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So I beg of you... Please, let us be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:36.61,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:38.48,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, not a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:39.96,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Their aura must be too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:46.36,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's no reason to exorcise them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:48.33,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,They said that they \Nwouldn't do anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.49,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,They're a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:50.34,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:53.05,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We called you here because we \Nneed you to exorcise them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:55.41,Main,College student B,0000,0000,0000,,It's way too creepy knowing they're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.86,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if they do anything bad or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:15:59.77,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, we said we'd pay you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.69,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and exorcise them already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.73,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting goosebumps just standing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.69,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's so creepy, \NI feel like I'm going to throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:07.87,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Mob?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:10.77,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten rid of plenty \Nof evil spirits before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:14.41,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,These people just want to live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:18.37,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... I don't want to destroy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:23.08,Main,College student B,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry up and do it already! \NNo one cares how you feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:29.15,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, we asked for your help \Nbecause we really needed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:33.01,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Our customers always take top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:39.43,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,However, if spirits deserve\Nas much respect as the living,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:43.81,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,and the three here are truly \Njust a family living peacefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:51.18,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can't make Mob do something as\Nheinous as barging in and dispatching them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:54.95,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,But our clients' fear is real, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.12,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:59.91,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,As a professional, can I really put \Nthe ghosts above the clients?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:01.63,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, man of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:05.75,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you've got plenty of \Npent-up spiritual power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:06.88,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Dimple?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:10.77,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,You gained that strength to \Nprotect your family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:12.51,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:15.97,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Why not kill those three right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:20.82,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,They won't have to exorcise you\Nif the clients are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.85,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,You want to live peacefully \Nwith your family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:30.32,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. What other choice do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.84,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.67,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:51.30,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you... Please let us be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:54.82,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot do something so horrific,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.26,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,especially in front of my child...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:59.22,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well, what're you gonna do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:02.78,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But we have nowhere left to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:06.30,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,If you must go through with it, \Nwe'll just have to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:08.58,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:12.42,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I ask that you \Nlet us all go together,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:14.57,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,wherever it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:18.70,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Mob, are the spirits still saying something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:25.15,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:27.24,Main,College Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... So what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:28.80,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,A moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:29.93,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mob?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:32.59,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,He's so against exorcising them\Nthat it's making him tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:34.41,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,That much, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:36.80,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it. Let's skip the exorcism.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:40.10,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm ordering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:42.90,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to listen to your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:46.16,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. You don't have to \Ntake this so seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:48.18,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,You're plenty strong, Shigeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.27,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:59.74,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,This must be something \Nthat only I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:04.24,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, there's no way I can\Ngo off my feelings alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.53,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:09.90,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,If I truly decide to protect this family,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:14.59,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,that'll mean the clients will\Nhave to get hurt instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.16,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,How long is this gonna take, damn it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:19.63,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares what the brat—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:25.26,Main,College student B,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, what the hell is this? Salt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:27.67,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,This concludes the exorcism.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:28.57,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:30.44,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:31.22,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,That was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.19,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,We're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.14,Main,College student A,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:39.28,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Reigen? What's the matter with you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:43.66,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what's going on here... \NWhy didn't I realize it sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:48.80,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,He can do so much more \Nthan an average person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.49,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,The world he can see \Nis far bigger than ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:55.75,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Curses and spirits are a \Npart of Mob's daily life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:20:01.72,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Both the human and the inhuman\Nare equally close to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.48,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:07.88,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because I took too many jobs,\Ngot complacent, and half-assed things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:12.45,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:16.13,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Want some soba?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.09,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.12,sign_4283_38_Spirits_and_Such,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\frz266\fs14\3c&H635F5B&\pos(419,60)}Spirits and Such Consultation Office
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:34.12,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,You okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:38.59,sign_29590_401_The_New_Star_of_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The New Star of the 21st Century
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:38.59,sign_29590_402_Reigen_Arataka,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Reigen Arataka
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:38.59,sign_29590_403_Spirits_and_Such,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits and Such Consultation Office
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:38.59,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,You actually took money for just\Nthrowing a bunch of salt around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:40.29,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,What was I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:43.27,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't taken the money, \Nit would've been suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:46.30,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, you're sure\Nthey weren't evil spirits, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.72,sign_29882_408_If_there_are_3_e,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,57)}If there are\N{\c&H2B352E&}3 evil spirits,\Nthe exorcism fee\Non 1 of them\Nwill be on the\Nhouse!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:50.62,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I tried to provoke him,\N but he didn't turn into an evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:51.27,sign_29882_408_If_there_are_3_e,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(278,1)}If there are\N{\c&H2B352E&}3 evil spirits,\Nthe exorcism fee\Non 1 of them\Nwill be on the\Nhouse!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:53.44,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Why are {\i1}you{\i0} trembling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:57.71,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're yawning. \NMan, you two are like night and day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:01.46,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've got something on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:02.19,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:05.16,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, someone definitely cursed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:07.39,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen to me if I leave it alone?
